                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7368demons">Ṣalot baʾǝnta wa-Bāryā wa-gānen wa-Ṣǝlwāgi wa-Mārtaññā
          wa-Tankʷǝlaññā ...</title>
                            <note>Written on the upper part of the scroll, in the left column and below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ <surplus>ወ</surplus>ባርያ፡ ወጋኔን፡ <sic>ወጽልዋጊ፡</sic>
                                ወማርተኛ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ወተ<supplied reason="omitted">ን</supplied>ኵለኛ፡
                                <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ታዖስ፡ አዜ፡ አዝያስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> በኃይለ፡ ዝንቱ፡ አንብቦ፡ ወአስተናግሮ፡ ለቡዳ፡ መሠርይ፡ ወለሌጌዎን፡
                                ኢኩይ፡ ለቍርፀት፡ ወለፍልፀት፡ ለዓይነት፡ ወለውግዓት፡ ለዛር፡ ወለንዳድ፡ ለቡዳ፡ ወለበዓለ፡ ግብር፡ ወለትግርትያ፡ ወሾቶላይ፡ ጋኔን፡ ወውርዝልያ፡ ወደባስ፡ ወአሶ፡ 
                                ወነቀጥቃጥ፡ ወቅርጥማት፡ ወአጽረ፡ ሽንት፡ ወአልጉም፡ ወጽልዋጊ፡ ወማርተኛ፡ ወተንኵነኛ፡ ወእከያኛ፡ ወስራይ፡ ወኵሉ፡ ደዌ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7374Zar">Ṣalota Zār qeqel betel robel</title>
                            <note>Written on the upper part of the scroll, in the left column and below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎተ፡ ዛር፡ ቄቄል፡ ቤቴል፡ ሮቤል፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4506Salam">Malkǝʾ-hymn to Our Lady Mary</title>
                            <note>Written on the upper part of the scroll, in the left column and below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለገጽኪ፡ ዘጥቀ፡ ይልሂ፡ እምስነ፡ ከዋክብት፡ ወርህ፡ ወእምስነ፡ ፀሐይ፡ መብርሂ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ኦእግዝዕትየ፡
                                ማርያም፡ <sic>አድኅንኒ፡</sic> እመክራ፡ ሥጋ፡ ወነፍስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6786MatthewEight">Matthew 8:28–32</title>
                            <note>Account of the healing by Jesus of the two possessed by demons in Mt. 8:28-34.</note>
                            <note>Written on the upper part of the scroll, in the middle column and below the upper picture.</note>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7365PrayerJesus">Yǝtnaśāʿ ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer wa-yǝzzaraw ḍaru ...</title>
                            <note>Written on the upper part of the scroll, in the right column and below the upper picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ይትነሣዕ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወይዘረው፡ ፀሩ፡ ወይጕየዩ፡ ፀላዕቱ፡ እምቅድመ፡
                                ገፁ፡ ሐተወ፡ አፍአተ፡ አንሣእኩ፡ አዕይንትየ፡ መንገለ፡ አድባር፡ እምአይቴ፡ ይምፃዕ፡ ረዲዖትየ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ኦአምላከ፡ ዳዊት፡ አድኅኖ፡
                                እምዕለት፡ ዕኪት፡ ወእምሠአታተ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ንዒ፡ ማርያም፡ ለዕውር፡ ብርሃኑ፡ ወንኢ፡ ድንግል፡ <surplus>ድንግል፡</surplus>
                                ለጽሙዕ፡ ዓንቅዕተ፡ ወይኑ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7042PrayerMichael">LIT7042PrayerMichael</title>
                            <note>Written on the middle part of the scroll, in the left column and below the second picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ <sic>ለ</sic>ጌዎን፡ ርኩስ፡ ዘይሰልብ፡ ልበ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወይመጽእ፡ ከመ፡ ጽላሎት፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                አምሐልኵከ፡ ወአወገዝኩከ፡ በ፫አካላት፡ ወበ፩መለኮት፡ ወበ፭ቅንዋተ፡ መስቀሉ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ለሥሃ፡ ኅምዙ፡ 
                                ለሞት፡ ወተቀጥጠ፡ ኃይሉ፡ ለሰይጣን፡ ቍርፀት፡ ወፍልጸት፡ ዓይነት፡ ውግዓት፡ ዛር፡ ወንዳድ፡ ቡዳ፡ ወበዓለ፡ ግብር፡ ወትግርትያ፡ አድኅኖ፡ ለገብርከ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7345SeddatSayt">Ṣalota baʾǝnta sǝddatomu la-sayṭānāt</title>
                            <note>Written on the middle part of the scroll, in the left column and below the second picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ስደቶሙ፡ ለሰይጣናት፡ ዝጋኔን፡ ይትሐረድ፡ ጶጶለጽኝ፡ ጨለጓፍ፡ 
                                <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ውጉዛነ፡ ይኩኑ፡ አጋንንት፡ ፀዋጋን፡ ወሰብዕ፡ መሠርያን<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> 
                                ወእምውግዓት፡ ሣቅሣቂያን፡ ወእምትግርቲያ፡ እቡያን፡ ወእምቡዳ፡ ቀታልያን፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4007Salotb">Ṣalot baʾǝnta maftǝḥe śǝrāy</title>
                            <note>Written on the middle part of the scroll, in the right column and below the second picture.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ስራይ፡ ዘተቀድሐ፡ እም፹ወ፩መፃሕፍት፡ ዘወጽአት፡ 
                                እምኢየሩሳሌም፡ ዘሞዖሙ፡ ለመሰርያን፡ ወለደጋምያነ፡ አስማት፡ ወለመታርያነ፡ ዕፅ፡ እስላም፡ ወክርስቲያን፡ ጋላ፡ ወሽንቅላ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                ፍታሕ፡ ክሙናዝር፡ ኤልናዝር፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ፍታሕ፡ ዘተገብረ፡ ወዘተደግመ፡ በነምር፡ ወበዝዕብ፡ ወበአንበሳ፡ ጋማ፡ ደጊሞሙ፡ ወበዘሆን፡ ሐሞት፡ 
                                ወበዘልበደ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሥጋ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i9">
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7344FethatSer">Ṣalota fǝtḥata sǝrāy ʾEfzāzewos</title>
                            <note>Prayer with a reference to Metropolitan <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8388SalamaI">Salāmā III</persName>, who died in 
                                <date when="1867">1867</date>.</note>
                            <note>Written on the lower part of the scroll, in the left column and below the third picture. </note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎተ፡ ፍትሐተ፡ ስራይ፡ ኤፍዛዜዎስ፡ ኤፍዛዜዎስ፡ ኤፍዛዜዎስ፡ መርታዳ፡ መርታዳ፡
                                መርታዳ፡ አክሎክ፡ አክሎክ፡ አክሎክ፡ ፍታሕ፡ ዳዊ፡ ፍታሕ፡ ጉሐኤል፡ ፍታሕ፡ ቀንተው፡ ፍታሕ፡ ቀርነለው፡ ዘፈታሕኮሙ፡ ለጴጥሮስ፡ ወለጳውሎሥ፡ እምዋቅሕተ፡
                                ብርት፡ አነኒ፡ ፈታሕኩ፡ ለንጉሥነ፡ መፍቀሬ፡ አምላክ፡ በጳጳስነ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8388SalamaI">አቡነ፡ ሰላማ፡</persName> ይትፈታሕ፡ 
                                ዝሥራይ፡ በላእለ፡ ገብርከ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
